## **1. Autentikasi**
- **POST** /api/auth/register: Mendaftar  
- **POST** /api/auth/login: Login  
- **POST** /api/auth/logout: Logout  
- **GET** /api/auth/check-token: Cek token  
## **2. User**
- **GET** /api/user/profile/{username}: Profil user  
- **GET** /api/user (Admin): Daftar user  
- **PUT** /api/user/profile/{username}: Update profil  
- **DELETE** /api/user/{username} (Admin): Hapus user  
## **3. Role (Admin)**
- **GET** /api/role: Daftar role  
- **POST** /api/role: Tambah role  
## **4. Room**
- **GET** /api/room: Daftar room  
- **GET** /api/room/{slug}: Detail room  
- **POST** /api/room (Admin): Tambah room  
- **PUT** /api/room/{slug} (Admin): Update room  
- **DELETE** /api/room/{slug} (Admin): Hapus room  
## **5. Post**
- **GET** /api/post: Daftar postingan  
- **GET** /api/post/{slug}: Detail postingan  
- **POST** /api/post: Tambah postingan  
- **PUT** /api/post/{slug}: Update postingan  
- **DELETE** /api/post/{slug} (Admin): Hapus postingan  
## **6. Comment**
- **GET** /api/post/{slug}/comment: Daftar komentar  
- **POST** /api/post/{slug}/comment: Tambah komentar  
- **PUT** /api/comment/{comment_id}: Update komentar  
- **DELETE** /api/comment/{comment_id}: Hapus komentar  
## **7. Like**
- **POST** /api/post/{slug}/like: Like postingan  
- **POST** /api/comment/{comment_id}/like: Like komentar  
- **DELETE** /api/post/{slug}/like: Hapus like postingan  
- **DELETE** /api/comment/{comment_id}/like: Hapus like komentar  
## **8. Bookmark**
- **GET** /api/bookmark: Daftar bookmark  
- **POST** /api/bookmark/{slug}: Tambah bookmark  
- **DELETE** /api/bookmark/{slug}: Hapus bookmark  
## **Admin Only**
- **GET** /api/user  
- **DELETE** /api/user/{username}  
- **POST** /api/roles  
- **POST** /api/room  
- **PUT** /api/room/{slug}  
- **DELETE** /api/room/{slug}  
- **DELETE** /api/post/{slug}
